cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with person re-identification using depth information. It may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it involves processing and analyzing visual data. Additionally, machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories are also likely as the paper proposes a new feature descriptor and transfer scheme. Finally, the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category may also be relevant as the paper deals with 3D depth data.
